## Package
Always import from `test-client-design-system`:
```tsx
import { Button, Text } from 'test-client-design-system';
import 'test-client-design-system/src/design-tokens/tokens.css';
```

## Design Token Rules
- NEVER hardcode hex colors — use CSS variables: `var(--color-primary)`
- NEVER hardcode font sizes — use CSS variables: `var(--font-heading-1-size)`
- For TypeScript access: `import { designTokens } from 'test-client-design-system'`

