### Button
  Button component
  Import: `import { Button } from 'test-client-design-system'`
  Props:
    - variant: 'default' | 'flat' | 'stroked' | 'basic' | 'icon' (optional) — The variant of the button.
- 'default': Standard button with background color.
- 'flat': Button with no background.
- 'stroked': Button with a border.
- 'basic': Basic button with minimal styling.
- 'icon': Button meant for icons.
    - size: 'small' | 'medium' | 'large' (optional) — The size of the button.
- 'small': Small button size.
- 'medium': Medium button size.
- 'large': Large button size.
    - disabled: boolean (optional) — If true, the button will be disabled.
    - className: string (optional) — Additional class names to apply to the button.

